<h4>Command line utility</h4>

<h5>Sample usage</h5>

<ul>
<li><code>color-world data.csv --unit=kg</code></li>
<li><code>color-world data.csv -o output.svg</code></li>
<li><code>cat data.csv | color-world &gt; output.svg </code></li>
</ul>

